Description:
For the last 2 decades, Power Solution has been empowering off-grid communities worldwide with affordable, durable, and sustainable one-stop solar solutions, committing ourselves to bringing light and electricity to poverty-stricken households while protecting our mother earth. Thus today, we are thrilled to report what we have achieved:

    50.07 Million People have started to enjoy the abundant benefits of solar-powered electricity;
    7.15 Million Households have been lit up and embraced the great convenience of modern society;
    65.07 Million KWH Electricity have been generated in a sustainable, responsible, and accessible style;
    17.81 Million Dollars in electricity charge have been saved for the betterment of life of the  impoverished;
    5.94 Million Tons of Carbon Emission have been averted from entering the atmosphere after replacing kerosene with solar energy;
    37,940 Children have been protected from respiratory diseases caused by candles and kerosene lamps;
    66 Countries have gained access to solar energy with decreased risk in safety, health, and economy brought by kerosene.

And we will not stop here. We believe that everyone has the right to enjoy light. With our innovation, the last mile is never unreachable.
For all and for good, we power on.

Fundada em 2023, a Associação Brasileira da Indústria do Hidrogênio Verde (ABIHV) é uma associação civil de direito privado, sem fins lucrativos, que congrega empresas atuantes em toda cadeia de valor do Hidrogênio Verde. 

A ABIHV tem como principal objetivo contribuir ativamente no desenvolvimento das condições necessárias para produção de Hidrogênio Verde e seus derivados de forma competitiva no Brasil, promovendo desenvolvimento econômico sustentável do país através da geração de renda, tecnologia e empregos; pautada por uma atuação diversa, inclusiva, socialmente responsável e reconhecida pela sociedade. 

Para tanto, a ABIHV atua para:
•	Incentivar a inserção e participação do Hidrogênio Verde e derivados na matriz energética brasileira;
•	Influenciar a formulação de políticas públicas voltadas ao setor, através da legítima representação de interesses frente aos órgãos do Poder Executivo e Legislativo, bem como Agências Reguladoras, nas esferas federal, estadual e municipal, bem como demais órgãos e associações que possam contribuir para o desenvolvimento do mercado de Hidrogênio Verde;
•	Organizar ações conjuntas de seus associados, tendo em vista a representatividade junto aos vários setores da sociedade brasileira e autoridades governamentais;
•	Buscar, junto aos setores financeiros (nacionais e internacionais), instrumentos de fomento a projetos relacionados à produção de Hidrogênio Verde e derivados;
•	Firmar convênios de cooperação a programas relacionados à produção de Hidrogênio Verde e derivados com instituições internacionais e nacionais e parcerias com agências de cooperação internacional e câmaras de fomento, que detenham pertinência temática frente aos objetivos da Associação;
•	Difundir conhecimento econômico e técnico sobre os usos e aplicações do Hidrogênio Verde e seus derivados.

WeLion is the pioneer in research and mass production of solid-state lithium-ion batteries. Usinginsitu-solidification technology, currently we produce semi-solid-state lithium battery as following:
Ø NCM 270&310 Wh/kg (16/22/27/30ah), applies for drones, eVTOL, Robots, marine, electric motorcycle;
Ø NCM 270 wh/kg, (22,31 ah), ESS type applied for potable power station;
Ø NCM 350 wh/kg, 106ah,  applied for premium electric vehicle (NIO);
ØLFP 150wh/kg, 45ah pouch form and 165wh/kg, 280ah, cubic form, applied for commercial & residential ESS and commercial vehicle.

Using breakthrough plasma-catalytic technology, we have designed a mobile CHP power plant for production of clean, CO2 – neutral, affordable electricity and heat from waste – mPower200. The design of mPower200 is unmatched for its compact size, reliability and simplicity of operations, as well as the cost of power produced. 

What makes this ultra-compact size possible is our plasma-catalytic reactor – SynGen – which replaces tons of gas cleaning equipment with a barrel-size device. SynGen converts even the highest level of tars and other pollutants in dirty gas from pyrolysis or gasification to clean synthesis gas – in one step and a with minimal energy input. Our proprietary plasma-catalytic reactors are the foundation for other related applications for the following types of CO2-neutral energy and products: 

- Green Hydrogen from natural gas without CO2 with high-value, super-clean, magnetic nanocarbon;
- Synthetic Waxes and Fuels from waste natural gas flared around the world;
- Chemical-free removal of H2S from natural gas and biogases;
- Green Hydrogen from waste biomass.

XEMC Group is one of the largest manufacturing complexes in China, which enjoys a history of more than 70 years and possesses more than 1000 patents and intellectual property rights. XEMC employs more than 10,000 people and operates businesses in manufacturing of electric machines, heavy trucks, ship propulsion systems, electric locomotives for mining industry, light rail vehicles for urban transportation, water pumps, equipment for national defense and wind turbines.
As one of the fastest growing business sectors in XEMC Group, the wind group is one of the two leading suppliers of direct drive turbines on the Chinese market. XEMC has produced and installed about 620 units of 2MW turbines. XEMC boasts a very healthy order book. The XEMC 2MW series turbines are, in China, the largest turbines in mass production. 
We offer advanced designs from a long Dutch heritage and of high design integrity. Direct Drive Permanent Magnet Generator (PMG) technology was started by Lagerwey in the Netherlands. Main features of our Direct Drive PMG wind turbines and XEMC can be summarized as follows, 
Lower service & maintenance costs (f.i. no gearbox, no oil leakage);
Top down –Bottom up Onshore & Offshore Turbine design;
Special purpose design converter for optimal grid stability (XV90)
High availability & high annual yield;
Active and continuous presence in NW Europe. Strong parent company;
High quality -low cost manufacturing including a partly Chinese supply chain;Competitive pricing;
Staying power of parent company
Low technological and economical risk profile.
Resulting in lowest total cost of ownership and highest I.R.R. during the 20 years of design lifetime.

Guangdong Cooli New Energy factory. 13 Years Professional Factory with 3 buildings. (Founded In 2010). With ISO Certification. We are a supplier and service provider of Rack/ABS Lithium Battery ; Wall Mounted Lithium Battery ; High volt/amp Lithium Battery ;  etc.  Excellent Quality : Use Grade A+ cells quality . Got IEC, CE, UN38.3, MSDS，ISO9001... Certificates.


Our advantages are followings:
1. Our cells are from China's top brands, such as EVE, CATL, GXHT, CALB, LISHEN, Various Battery cell in stock ;
2. The BMS system is developed by our own factory, matching is very good;
