In summary, our factory can provide very good support in terms of price, quality and production time.

Resources Technology Co., Ltd (SRP for short) is a high-tech enterprise focusing on the R&D, manufacturing and sales of energy storage inverters and LFP battery systems. The company was founded in 2006 and headquartered in Jinan. Funded by a listed company MOSO group, the core team of the enterprise is composed of domestic leading technical talents and senior experts in power electronics technology.

SRP is focusing on four application scenarios:
Residential energy storage system;
C&I energy storage system;
Multipurpose LFP Battery application;
Photovoltaic grid-connected power station.

SRP provides customers with standard energy storage products and customized solutions.

Welcome to the planet of OMNIA structures. 
 
Patented in 1996, after three years of operation under the "Bottega del ferro" brand, we created OMNIA SPATIAL STRUCTURES, a leader company designing, producing and creating grid structures for roofs and projecting roofs.
 
Backed by our experience in the roofing industry, in 2011 Omnia Spatial Structures patented a new laying system for solar and photovoltaic panels which allows installing a system without drilling the roof: "Omniablok".

Which are the Omnia Structures advantages? 
- Great strength little weight;
- Ampliable and re-modulable;
- Transport practicatilty;
- Solar panels structure: mounting system for photovoltaic panels without drilling roof.

